    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《秘境战盟》是一款设定在奇幻世界中的多人在线地下城冒险（MODA）游戏，拥有无限扩展的地下城挑战。玩家必须专注于团队合作，重视技巧、协作和策略，才能击败强大的Boss、获取丰厚的战利品，并共同克服无处不在的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验经典的“铁三角”玩法，组建由坦克、治疗和输出组成的终极团队，击败成群的敌人和强大的Boss。与朋友们一起合作，克服终极挑战，创造牢不可破的羁绊和难忘的时刻。玩家还可以在竞争排行榜上展示个人实力，争夺《秘境战盟》的最高荣誉。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/efa2b0b994a86b402f293ad3c35a927b.poster.avif?t=1772113228\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/efa2b0b994a86b402f293ad3c35a927b.webm?t=1772113228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/efa2b0b994a86b402f293ad3c35a927b.mp4?t=1772113228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坚持不懈，战胜困难，冲击《秘境战盟》英雄榜的巅峰！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组建完美团队</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个充满强大敌人和丰富奖励的奇幻世界中，与朋友们组队进行4人合作的多人游戏。在众多坦克、治疗和输出角色中切换，运用独特的技能组合，打造完美平衡的团队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/a3c2383b4ee7e5f57db1dca756be7ada.poster.avif?t=1772113228\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/a3c2383b4ee7e5f57db1dca756be7ada.webm?t=1772113228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/a3c2383b4ee7e5f57db1dca756be7ada.mp4?t=1772113228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无限升级的可重玩性</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次探险都会带来全新的挑战，地下城难度会随着玩家的进阶而提升。通过季节性更新、地下城修正、新功能和奖励，游戏将保持新鲜与刺激，增加多层级的可重玩性。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/a2afa49b32e2319914a42fefa9b3cd43.poster.avif?t=1772113228\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/a2afa49b32e2319914a42fefa9b3cd43.webm?t=1772113228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/a2afa49b32e2319914a42fefa9b3cd43.mp4?t=1772113228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的奖励、战利品和装备 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次完成地下城探险，玩家都会获得装备以提升角色实力！探险难度越高，奖励越丰厚。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/bdefa254fc91bb7d2cb6028b5091159f.poster.avif?t=1772113228\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/bdefa254fc91bb7d2cb6028b5091159f.webm?t=1772113228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/bdefa254fc91bb7d2cb6028b5091159f.mp4?t=1772113228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特而复杂的Boss机制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个Boss都有独特且多样的机制，每次挑战都是一次全新的体验。敌人的技能会随着难度提升而增强，额外的难度修正将持续带来挑战，让玩家在成长和提升中不断面对新的难题。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/fc94a6dd040110df463a47701ab7573f.poster.avif?t=1772113228\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/fc94a6dd040110df463a47701ab7573f.webm?t=1772113228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352620/extras/fc94a6dd040110df463a47701ab7573f.mp4?t=1772113228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
